
== Malaki achem Pustok ==
'''Book of Malachi'''
[[File:Gustave Doré Malachiáš 3.1.jpg|thumb|Illustration of the coming of [[God]]'s Messenger in 3:1, by Franciszek Żmurko.]]
[[File:Duccio di Buoninsegna 066.jpg|thumb|left|The Prophet Malachi, painting by Duccio di Buoninsegna, c. 1310 (Museo dell'Opera del Duomo, Siena Cathedral).]]

Malaki Israelacho nimanno provadi. Krista adim panchvea xenkddeachea modlea vorsamnim, Esdra ani Nehemia hanchea disamnim, to jielo. Malaki poile suvater Judev iadnikanchim ani porjechim patkam tanchea tonddar marta ani dusre suvater Mesiachea kallaili Devachi nit porgott korta. To darunn xirapam ani dhomkavnneam vorvim aplo sondex porgott’tta ani aple porjek koslich buzvonn dina. Hea provadiachea disamnim Judev lok bhaileanuch kaide pallit pun bhitorlean tanchim kallzam Deva sorxilim pois aslim.


